{
  "video_id": "rtcrqLWZr_0",
  "title": "How to win at evolution and survive a mass extinction | Lauren Sallan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13320.0,
      "end_time": 14399.0,
      "text": "Congratulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14721.0,
      "end_time": 15921.0,
      "text": "By being here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15945.0,
      "end_time": 17382.0,
      "text": "listening, alive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17406.0,
      "end_time": 19707.0,
      "text": "a member of a growing species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19731.0,
      "end_time": 22692.0,
      "text": "you are one of history&#39;s greatest winners --"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22716.0,
      "end_time": 27136.0,
      "text": "the culmination of a success story four billion years in the making."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27768.0,
      "end_time": 29899.0,
      "text": "You are life&#39;s one percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30884.0,
      "end_time": 32400.0,
      "text": "The losers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32640.0,
      "end_time": 34896.0,
      "text": "the 99 percent of species who have ever lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34920.0,
      "end_time": 36860.0,
      "text": "are dead --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36110.0,
      "end_time": 39471.0,
      "text": "killed by fire, flood, asteroids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39495.0,
      "end_time": 41796.0,
      "text": "predation, starvation, ice, heat"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41820.0,
      "end_time": 44600.0,
      "text": "and the cold math of natural selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45186.0,
      "end_time": 46386.0,
      "text": "Your ancestors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46410.0,
      "end_time": 47959.0,
      "text": "back to the earliest fishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47984.0,
      "end_time": 50750.0,
      "text": "overcame all these challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50932.0,
      "end_time": 53901.0,
      "text": "You are here because of golden opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53925.0,
      "end_time": 56589.0,
      "text": "made possible by mass extinction."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57437.0,
      "end_time": 60683.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61480.0,
      "end_time": 62199.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62223.0,
      "end_time": 65452.0,
      "text": "The same is true of your co-winners and relatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65476.0,
      "end_time": 68164.0,
      "text": "The 34,000 kinds of fishes."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68586.0,
      "end_time": 70686.0,
      "text": "How did we all get so lucky?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70710.0,
      "end_time": 72342.0,
      "text": "Will we continue to win?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73278.0,
      "end_time": 77233.0,
      "text": "I am a fish paleobiologist who uses big data --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77257.0,
      "end_time": 78466.0,
      "text": "the fossil record --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78490.0,
      "end_time": 81720.0,
      "text": "to study how some species win and others lose."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82880.0,
      "end_time": 83698.0,
      "text": "The living can&#39;t tell us;"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83722.0,
      "end_time": 85422.0,
      "text": "they know nothing but winning."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85446.0,
      "end_time": 87390.0,
      "text": "So, we must speak with the dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87946.0,
      "end_time": 89667.0,
      "text": "How do we make dead fishes talk?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90265.0,
      "end_time": 94678.0,
      "text": "Museums contain multitudes of beautiful fish fossils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94702.0,
      "end_time": 96482.0,
      "text": "but their real beauty emerges"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96506.0,
      "end_time": 100753.0,
      "text": "when combined with the larger number of ugly, broken fossils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100777.0,
      "end_time": 102918.0,
      "text": "and reduced to ones and zeros."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103327.0,
      "end_time": 107723.0,
      "text": "I can trawl a 500-million-year database for evolutionary patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108412.0,
      "end_time": 109566.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109590.0,
      "end_time": 113337.0,
      "text": "fish forms can be captured by coordinates"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113361.0,
      "end_time": 117467.0,
      "text": "and transformed to reveal major pathways of change"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117491.0,
      "end_time": 119610.0,
      "text": "and trends through time."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120583.0,
      "end_time": 122920.0,
      "text": "Here is the story of the winners and losers"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122944.0,
      "end_time": 127770.0,
      "text": "of just one pivotal event I discovered using fossil data."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127500.0,
      "end_time": 131972.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s travel back 360 million years --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131996.0,
      "end_time": 135536.0,
      "text": "six times as long ago as the last dinosaur --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135560.0,
      "end_time": 137206.0,
      "text": "to the Devonian period;"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137230.0,
      "end_time": 138614.0,
      "text": "a strange world."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139505.0,
      "end_time": 143366.0,
      "text": "Armored predators with razor-edge jaws dominated"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143390.0,
      "end_time": 147512.0,
      "text": "alongside huge fishes with arm bones in their fins."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149106.0,
      "end_time": 152358.0,
      "text": "Crab-like fishes scuttled across the sea floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153278.0,
      "end_time": 156761.0,
      "text": "The few ray-fin relatives of salmon and tuna"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156785.0,
      "end_time": 159269.0,
      "text": "cowered at the bottom of the food chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160217.0,
      "end_time": 163713.0,
      "text": "The few early sharks lived offshore in fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164900.0,
      "end_time": 168652.0,
      "text": "Your few four-legged ancestors, the tetrapods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168676.0,
      "end_time": 171147.0,
      "text": "struggled in tropical river plains."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172391.0,
      "end_time": 174102.0,
      "text": "Ecosystems were crowded."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174744.0,
      "end_time": 176599.0,
      "text": "There was no escape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176623.0,
      "end_time": 178375.0,
      "text": "no opportunity in sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179110.0,
      "end_time": 180496.0,
      "text": "Then the world ended."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 180888.0,
      "end_time": 182838.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182862.0,
      "end_time": 184227.0,
      "text": "No, it is a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184251.0,
      "end_time": 188619.0,
      "text": "96 percent of all fish species died"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 188643.0,
      "end_time": 193103.0,
      "text": "during the Hangenberg event, 359 million years ago:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193127.0,
      "end_time": 195135.0,
      "text": "an interval of fire and ice."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195516.0,
      "end_time": 198511.0,
      "text": "A crowded world was disrupted and swept away."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199735.0,
      "end_time": 202236.0,
      "text": "Now, you might think that&#39;s the end of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204451.0,
      "text": "The mighty fell, the meek inherited the earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204475.0,
      "end_time": 205680.0,
      "text": "and here we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206660.0,
      "end_time": 208929.0,
      "text": "But winning is not that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210168.0,
      "end_time": 213333.0,
      "text": "The handful of survivors came from many groups --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213357.0,
      "end_time": 216303.0,
      "text": "all greatly outnumbered by their own dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216327.0,
      "end_time": 219600.0,
      "text": "They ranged from top predator to bottom-feeder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219840.0,
      "end_time": 220384.0,
      "text": "big to small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 220408.0,
      "end_time": 222381.0,
      "text": "marine to freshwater."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222405.0,
      "end_time": 224397.0,
      "text": "The extinction was a filter."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224421.0,
      "end_time": 226606.0,
      "text": "It merely leveled the playing field."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227352.0,
      "end_time": 232770.0,
      "text": "What really counted was what survivors did over the next several million years"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232794.0,
      "end_time": 234575.0,
      "text": "in that devastated world."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 236330.0,
      "end_time": 238803.0,
      "text": "The former overlords should have had an advantage."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 239245.0,
      "end_time": 241850.0,
      "text": "They became even larger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 241109.0,
      "end_time": 242503.0,
      "text": "storing energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 242527.0,
      "end_time": 244149.0,
      "text": "investing in their young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 244174.0,
      "end_time": 245836.0,
      "text": "spreading across the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245860.0,
      "end_time": 247329.0,
      "text": "feasting on fishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247353.0,
      "end_time": 250467.0,
      "text": "keeping what had always worked, and biding their time."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250906.0,
      "end_time": 253923.0,
      "text": "Yet they merely persisted for a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253947.0,
      "end_time": 255994.0,
      "text": "declining without innovating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 256170.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258279.00000000003,
      "text": "becoming living fossils."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258887.0,
      "end_time": 260848.0,
      "text": "They were too stuck in their ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 260872.0,
      "end_time": 262780.0,
      "text": "and are now largely forgotten."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 264366.0,
      "end_time": 269525.0,
      "text": "A few of the long-suffering ray-fins, sharks and four-legged tetrapods"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 269549.0,
      "end_time": 271203.0,
      "text": "went the opposite direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 271528.0,
      "end_time": 273240.0,
      "text": "They became smaller --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 273264.0,
      "end_time": 275840.0,
      "text": "living fast, dying young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275108.0,
      "end_time": 277172.0,
      "text": "eating little and reproducing rapidly."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277687.0,
      "end_time": 279654.0,
      "text": "They tried new foods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279678.0,
      "end_time": 280883.0,
      "text": "different homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 280907.0,
      "end_time": 283258.0,
      "text": "strange heads and weird bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 283282.0,
      "end_time": 284464.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 284488.0,
      "end_time": 287448.0,
      "text": "And they found opportunity, proliferated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 287472.0,
      "end_time": 291426.0,
      "text": "and won the future for their 60,000 living species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 291451.0,
      "end_time": 292822.0,
      "text": "including you."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 292846.0,
      "end_time": 294465.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why they look familiar."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 294489.0,
      "end_time": 295926.0,
      "text": "You know their names."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 297635.0,
      "end_time": 300111.0,
      "text": "Winning is not about random events"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 300136.0,
      "end_time": 301595.0,
      "text": "or an arms race."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 301619.0,
      "end_time": 305881.0,
      "text": "Rather, survivors went down alternative, evolutionary pathways."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306294.0,
      "end_time": 308818.0,
      "text": "Some found incredible success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 308843.0,
      "end_time": 311310.0,
      "text": "while others became dead fish walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312572.0,
      "end_time": 314885.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 314909.0,
      "end_time": 316516.0,
      "text": "A real scientific term."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 316540.0,
      "end_time": 318723.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318747.0,
      "end_time": 319915.0,
      "text": "I am now investigating"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319939.0,
      "end_time": 323632.0,
      "text": "how these pathways to victory and defeat repeat across time."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324750.0,
      "end_time": 328197.0,
      "text": "My lab has already compiled thousands upon thousands of dead fishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 328221.0,
      "end_time": 329869.0,
      "text": "but many more remain."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 329893.0,
      "end_time": 331750.0,
      "text": "However, it is already clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 331774.0,
      "end_time": 335454.0,
      "text": "that your ancestors&#39; survival through mass extinction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 335478.0,
      "end_time": 337922.0,
      "text": "and their responses in the aftermath"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 337946.0,
      "end_time": 339878.0,
      "text": "made you who you are today."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 340262.0,
      "end_time": 342381.0,
      "text": "What does this tell us for the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 342405.0,
      "end_time": 345159.0,
      "text": "As long as a handful of species survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 345183.0,
      "end_time": 347257.0,
      "text": "life will recover."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 347281.0,
      "end_time": 351154.0,
      "text": "The versatile and the lucky will not just replace what was lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 351178.0,
      "end_time": 352753.0,
      "text": "but win in new forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 353121.0,
      "end_time": 355551.0,
      "text": "It just might take several million years."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 356639.0,
      "end_time": 357789.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 357813.0,
      "end_time": 362491.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}